    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine is strong, the transmission is smooth, and all major mechanical systems are in great working order. While there are some minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with regular use\u2014such as a few light scratches on the exterior and slight wear on the driver's seat upholstery\u2014the car remains very presentable and reliable. It features a clean interior, updated tires, and a complete service history, making it a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
