    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project with this diamond in the rough! While this vehicle currently needs significant mechanical work and some TLC for the exterior, it represents a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for a restoration enthusiast or anyone looking for a fixer-upper with potential. It's an honest car at an honest price, perfect for someone who loves to bring a classic back to life!",
      "price": 4500.0,
