      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a history of meticulous maintenance and uncompromising care. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, affirms its status as a premier investment for the discerning driver. We invite you to experience the pinnacle of pre-owned excellence.",
      "price": 44900.0,
